' |              p2          Description of parameter 2.                       |
' | TRACING    : Set the WSHTRACE Windows environment variable to the level    |
' |              (1-n) of tracing you would like to capture.                   |
' | USAGE      :                                                               |
' |                                                                            |
' |              cscript Template.vbs "p1" "p2" //NoLogo                       |
